HEADWORD: Jingal
<hw>Jin*gal"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hind.
<ets>jang⟦amac⟧l</ets> a swivel, a large musket.]</ety> <def>A small
portable piece of ordnance, mounted on a swivel.</def> <altsp>[Written
also <asp>gingal</asp> and <asp>jingall</asp>.]</altsp>
<mark>[India]</mark>⟦br⟧
